---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Responsible Gambling | Read Between Bets"
  description="Responsible gambling principles and support resources."
  locale="ru"
  alternates={{ en: '/responsible-gambling/', ru: '/ru/responsible-gambling/' }}
>
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="section-padding max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Responsible Gambling</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p>Gambling should stay entertainment, not an income plan.</p>
        <h2>Warning signs</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Spending more time or money than planned</li>
          <li>Chasing losses</li>
          <li>Hiding gambling behavior from family or friends</li>
          <li>Harm to work, studies, finances, or relationships</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Safer-play tools</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Deposit and loss limits</li>
          <li>Time limits and reminders</li>
          <li>Self-exclusion</li>
          <li>Reality checks</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Support</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://www.gamblingtherapy.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">gamblingtherapy.org</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.gamcare.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">gamcare.org.uk</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.begambleaware.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">begambleaware.org</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
